When I wont the duel, my Mage friend had dinged 60 and I was 59… he started the fight by using Banish on my pet… VERY tough to beat a Mage while tanking his Epic pet heheh… but I got him. I landed a Vexing Mordinia (1k lifetap DOT) on him, then tanked his pet for a short while and channeled off one lifetap, then trew up a DA spell and DA tanked his pet while my lifetap DOT healed me and took him a little below 50%.. when the DA wore off I was at full health and full mana, I channeled off a few lifetaps and it was over. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
